sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant User as Client (User)
    participant GW as Ingress Gateway
    participant Kafka as Kafka (Event Bus)
    participant VAD as VAD Service
    participant ASR as ASR Service
    participant MT as Translation Service
    participant TTS as TTS Service

    Note over User, GW: WebSocket Connection Established

    %% Ingress Flow
    User->>GW: Stream Audio Chunk (Binary)
    GW->>GW: Wrap in AudioInputEvent (Avro)
    GW->>Kafka: Produce to 'audio.ingress'
    
    %% VAD Processing
    Kafka->>VAD: Consume 'audio.ingress'
    VAD->>VAD: Detect Speech Activity
    VAD->>Kafka: Produce 'speech_segment' (Target Topic)

    %% ASR Processing
    Kafka->>ASR: Consume 'speech_segment'
    ASR->>ASR: Transcribe (Whisper)
    ASR->>Kafka: Produce 'asr.text'

    %% Translation Processing
    Kafka->>MT: Consume 'asr.text'
    MT->>MT: Translate (NLLB)
    MT->>Kafka: Produce 'translation.text'

    %% TTS Processing
    Kafka->>TTS: Consume 'translation.text'
    TTS->>TTS: Synthesize (Kokoro)
    TTS->>Kafka: Produce 'tts.audio'

    %% Egress Flow
    Kafka->>GW: Consume 'tts.audio'
    GW->>User: Send Audio Chunk (WebSocket)